set.seed(1011)
train=sample(1:nrow(facebook), 250)
facebook.test=facebook[-train,]
High.test=High[-train]
tree.facebook=tree(High~.-Category,facebook,subset=train)
tree.pred=predict(tree.facebook,facebook.test,type="class")
table(tree.pred,High.test)
